content.rendered:
The MAXTRAX XTRACT INSERT TOOL is designed to make replacing damaged teeth in your MAXTRAX X SERIES 4wd Recovery Tracks a safe, simple, quick and easy task.

The socket of the MAXTRAX XTRACT INSERT TOOL fits all MAXTRAX MOUNTING PINS to make turning the locking knuckles easy.

Note: This product is not compatible with MAXTRAX MKII Recovery Tracks.
